verbose_text: In one pilot clinical study with 18 lesions from 7 breast cancer patients, the kinetics of [18 F] fluciclatide has been established by using a two-tissue reversible binding model, the k 3 / k 4 ratio was found to be a reasonable measure of specific binding, which suggests that this index could be used for estimating alpha v beta 3 expression in cancer lesions XREF_BIBR.
